1
00:00:04.070 --> 00:00:07.880
Our main tip on how to improve your study preparation 
time is to use pre-reading techniques.

2
00:00:07.910 --> 00:00:11.570
Before you start reading a text, it is essential 
that you complete a thorough pre-reading.

3
00:00:11.570 --> 00:00:15.340
You pre-read in order to get an overall view: 
What is the topic of the text?

4
00:00:15.350 --> 00:00:17.810
How is it constructed? How difficult is it to read?

5
00:00:17.870 --> 00:00:22.160
And last, but not least, what will you use it for? 
What is YOUR intention with reading the text?

6
00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:26.120
Maybe your teacher has emphasised topics or 
concepts you need to pay special attention to. 

7
00:00:25.520 --> 00:00:26.120


8
