9
00:00:30.420 --> 00:00:34.010
If you start reading a text without a clearly stated purpose,

10
00:00:34.010 --> 00:00:37.880
you can easily end up reading without

11
00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:40.370
direction and lose track of the intention.

12
00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:46.040
When you do a pre-reading, you check out 
the frontpage, the back page,

13
00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:50.930
table of contents, illustrations, headlines, 
graphics, illustrations, etc.

14
00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:55.160
This will give you a general overview and 
activate your prior subject knowledge

15
00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:59.750
and most likely help you to better comprehend 
and remember the text.

